    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish with a professional ceramic coating, entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains supple and matte, showing zero wear or bolster creasing, and the interior still carries a faint new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, documenting a history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-grade vehicle that requires absolutely no apologies.",
